{
  "stem": "2684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I-- I went to school in the usual way, the-- the usual four years of elementary school, and-- and four years of-- of middle class, what we called.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And before the war, I enrolled two years on the Jewish technical college, we can call it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after the war, I finished another two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I finished, more or less, a technical college course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And before the war, our religious life was my father was involved in the Jewish community, and he was also involved in-- in her-- in his profession.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was the president of the Hungarian Poultry Association, if you could call it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The translation is more or less like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were a-- a middle class family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My father was well known in the area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And to me, as a child, I-- I grew up with-- with football, actually, soccer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I call it football.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was our main entertainment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "After school, we went to the park and played till 6 o'clock, 7 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now, the family, I had a lot of first cousins, because of the-- of that three daughters of-- of my grandmother, which means my father had three sisters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And-- and my grandfather died very, very young age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So my father raised the-- the-- himself and the three sisters, plus my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was the breadwinner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So he didn't go much to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And financially, we were quite well off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I never knew anything which I wanted I wouldn't get.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, those days, the values were different of today's.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "If you had a-- a-- a little football with your grandmother's stockings and newspaper inside, that-- that was already a-- a wealth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- and that's how we lived up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We went to the swimming pools.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
